---
---
<section>
  <div class="section-label">What's included</div>
  <div class="included-grid">

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2.8 9a10 10 0 0 1 18.4 0"/><path d="M2.8 15a10 10 0 0 0 18.4 0"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Tournament-Grade Balls</div>
        <div class="included-desc">We never play more than 3 to 4 hours with the same balls. Experts recommend replacing after 8 to 9 hours of play. You always play with balls that have bounce and feel.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M8 2h8"/><path d="M9 2v2.789a4 4 0 0 1-.672 2.219l-.656.984A4 4 0 0 0 7 10.212V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h6a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-9.788a4 4 0 0 0-.672-2.219l-.656-.984A4 4 0 0 1 15 4.789V2"/><line x1="7" y1="15" x2="17" y2="15"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Bottled Mineral Water</div>
        <div class="included-desc">Bottled mineral water waiting at the courts every session. Nothing to sort, nothing to pay for.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="21"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Two Dedicated Courts</div>
        <div class="included-desc">Both courts, every weeknight. No sharing, no waiting, no wondering if courts are free.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Organised Play</div>
        <div class="included-desc">A dedicated Day Leader manages scheduling, rotations, and daily registration. You just bring your racket.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Consistency &amp; Club Feel</div>
        <div class="included-desc">Play with the same competitive players every week. Your game improves faster when you know who you are playing with and what to expect.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Tournaments &amp; Social Events</div>
        <div class="included-desc">PCI runs internal tournaments across groups and venues, seeded by your leaderboard ranking. Once a month, the group gets together off the court.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M15 10l4.553-2.069A1 1 0 0 1 21 8.82v6.36a1 1 0 0 1-1.447.889L15 14"/><rect x="1" y="6" width="15" height="12" rx="2"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Game Footage</div>
        <div class="included-desc">Professional cameras on every court. Watch your sessions back, track your improvement, and share highlights straight to your social media. Your best shots, on record.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="included-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="included-title">Welcome Kit</div>
        <div class="included-desc">A curated set of personalised PCI goodies, sent to every new member when they join.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
